{"file_name": "Architect_multipage.pdf", "file_type": "pdf", "confidence": 0.77, "time_taken": 0.84, "memory_mb": 4.4, "units": [{"index": 1, "method": "structured", "confidence": 0.78, "text": {"text": "AR. AMIT KAPOOR\nSenior Architect / Urban Design Specialist\nBengaluru, India | amit.kapoor@email.com | +91-9XXXXXXXXX\nPROFESSIONAL SUMMARY\nSenior Architect with over 12 years of experience in architectural design, urban planning, and project execution\nacross residential, commercial, and mixed-use developments. Proven expertise in concept design, client\ncoordination, statutory approvals, and on-site execution. Strong focus on sustainable design practices, cost\noptimization, and timely delivery of high-quality architectural solutions.\nCORE SKILLS\n(cid:127) Architectural Design & Planning\n(cid:127) Urban Design & Master Planning\n(cid:127) Sustainable & Green Building Design\n(cid:127) Construction Documentation\n(cid:127) Client & Consultant Coordination\n(cid:127) Project Scheduling & Site Supervision\n(cid:127) AutoCAD, Revit, SketchUp, Lumion\n(cid:127) Building Codes & Regulatory Compliance\nPROFESSIONAL EXPERIENCE\nSenior Architect \u2013 Horizon Design Studio (2018 \u2013 Present)\n(cid:127) Lead architectural design and execution for residential and commercial projects ranging from 50,000 to 500,000\nsq. ft.\n(cid:127) Developed concept designs, detailed drawings, and 3D visualizations in coordination with clients and\nconsultants.\n(cid:127) Managed statutory approvals with local authorities and ensured compliance with building codes and regulations.\n(cid:127) Supervised on-site execution and resolved design and construction issues to ensure timely project delivery\nwithin budget.", "tables": []}}, {"index": 2, "method": "structured", "confidence": 0.76, "text": {"text": "Architect \u2013 UrbanForm Architects (2012 \u2013 2018)\n(cid:127) Prepared detailed working drawings, BOQs, and construction documents for residential and commercial\nprojects.\n(cid:127) Coordinated with structural, MEP, and landscape consultants for integrated project delivery.\n(cid:127) Conducted regular site visits to monitor quality, progress, and adherence to design intent.\n(cid:127) Assisted in sustainable design strategies including daylight analysis, material optimization, and energy-efficient\nsolutions.\nKEY PROJECTS\n(cid:127) Mixed-use Commercial Complex \u2013 4,00,000 sq. ft.\n(cid:127) Luxury Residential Tower \u2013 32 storeys\n(cid:127) Corporate Office Campus \u2013 LEED Gold Certified\nEDUCATION\n(cid:127) Bachelor of Architecture (B.Arch) \u2013 School of Planning & Architecture, Delhi\nPROFESSIONAL AFFILIATIONS\n(cid:127) Council of Architecture (COA), India\n(cid:127) Indian Institute of Architects (IIA)\nADDITIONAL INFORMATION\n(cid:127) Strong presentation and visualization skills\n(cid:127) Experience working on fast-track projects\n(cid:127) Passionate about sustainable and context-driven design", "tables": []}}], "error": null, "embedding": [-0.0008298793691210449, 0.0019520199857652187, 0.018681103363633156, -0.01004606019705534, 0.04027194902300835, 0.00022242376871872693, 0.026537830010056496, 0.020053662359714508, 0.0009469349170103669, -0.028903720900416374, -0.03869813308119774, -0.00789810810238123, -0.05535062029957771, 0.020891588181257248, 0.062168944627046585, 0.04736959934234619, 0.0339323915541172, -0.0198837760835886, 0.03449266403913498, 0.00824698619544506, 0.04528796672821045, 0.007229035720229149, -0.006501967087388039, 0.06297643482685089, 0.009878421202301979, -0.03443345054984093, 0.00732599338516593, 0.023677902296185493, -0.06825850903987885, -0.039337143301963806, 0.016664734110236168, -0.030749771744012833, -0.03281289339065552, -0.03783949464559555, 0.004260672256350517, -0.015013404190540314, -0.031428247690200806, 0.00413247337564826, -0.007204168941825628, -0.02301960438489914, -0.015006931498646736, -0.034780167043209076, -0.0006369418697431684, -0.029141513630747795, -0.05336527898